    "summary": "The user, who has chronic kidney disease (CKD), asks for advice on treating a headache. The assistant correctly identifies the danger of ibuprofen for CKD patients and suggests acetaminophen (Tylenol) as a safer alternative while repeatedly emphasizing the necessity of consulting a nephrologist.",
